title: Sarina Wiegman 'really hurt' by World Cup kiss row
description: England coach Sarina Wiegman has said the crisis surrounding the World Cup kiss after Spain's win against her team in the final "really hurts" her as a wife, mother, coach and human being.

title: Devastated residents left homeless and helpless after one of worst fires in South African history

title: Anonymous buyer of world's largest whisky bottle revealed
